### CZ: Two scratcpads
# Manual scratchpad management
bindsym $mod+Shift+m mark mscratch, move scratchpad
bindsym $mod+m [con_mark="^mscratch$"] scratchpad show
bindsym $mod+Shift+n mark nscratch, move scratchpad
bindsym $mod+n [con_mark="nscratch"] scratchpad show

